'''大荔人'''头骨化石是[[中国|中国]][[华北地区|华北地区]][[旧石器时代|旧石器时代]]的早期[[智人|智人]]化石。发现于[[陕西省|陕西省]][[渭南市|渭南市]][[大荔县|大荔县]]解放村附近的洛河第三阶地砂砾层之中。
{{cladogram|align=left|title=人类亲缘树|caption=来源：Ni ''et al.'', 2021<ref name=Ni2021>{{cite journal |first1=X. |last1=Ni |first2=Q. |last2=Ji |first3=W. |last3=Wu |display-authors=et al. |year=2021 |title=Massive cranium from Harbin in northeastern China establishes a new Middle Pleistocene human lineage |journal=Innovation |doi=10.1016/j.xinn.2021.100130 |url=https://www.cell.com/the-innovation/fulltext/S2666-6758(21)00055-2 |access-date=2021-06-26 |archive-date=2021-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210705035455/https://www.cell.com/the-innovation/fulltext/S2666-6758(21)00055-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref>|cladogram={{clade
